---

### Azure CLI Authentication

Ensure you're logged into Azure CLI:
```bash
az login
az account show
```

### PowerShell Core Required

This agent requires PowerShell Core (pwsh), not Windows PowerShell. Verify:
```bash
pwsh --version
```
